- The Career Academies with our kids

00:00:27.884 --> 00:00:32.326
being naturally interested
in Math and Sciences and Art,

00:00:32.326 --> 00:00:34.951
it's been a very positive
experience for them.

00:00:34.951 --> 00:00:39.118
It's very been, very supportive
of their natural abilities.

00:00:41.343 --> 00:00:44.551
- Waterloo Schools really
prepared them for the life

00:00:44.551 --> 00:00:46.398
after they graduated from high school.

00:00:46.398 --> 00:00:48.867
They prepared them to go on to AP classes

00:00:48.867 --> 00:00:50.895
whatever their first choice
was to get into college,

00:00:50.895 --> 00:00:52.478
they got into them.

