- What I really like is it
prepares them for college

00:00:58.749 --> 00:01:03.156
in a way that I think is
gonna make them competitive

00:01:03.156 --> 00:01:07.470
with students from not
just other parts of Iowa

00:01:07.470 --> 00:01:11.637
but all other parts of the
United States and the world.

